Introduction

Lucky J (Korean: 럭키제이; Japanese: ラッキージェイ) was a hip-hop group under YMC Entertainment. They debuted on July 17, 2014 with the single "Can You Hear Me."

In August 2016, Jessi announced that Lucky J disbanded.
